Invocation Name: map four health
Developer Terms of Use
des:
The map4health skill allows you to connect your Amazon Alexa-enabled device with your map4health account so you can easily add your weight, blood glucose and blood pressure by simply asking Alexa. You can also ask map4health for a health tip whenever you like!

NOTE: The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
